| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5042 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 37564db4-9abc-57fc-8bf4-4d6bfa4c9296"
